description:
WOW!!! Over 1000 subscribers already!

I try to celebrate the milestone event by planting a tree and then trying to blow it up in some needlessly complicated, yet epic, manner. 

The party kinda falls apart when our guest of honor refuses to go to his special seat, and raises a hissy fit.

I've already started to plan our next party for if / when I hit 2500 subscribers. It'll be off the hook!

BTW: After watching the video, it seems the creeper was refusing to move because a block was missing in his path where the torch was attached to the tree.
fulltitle: Let's Play Minecraft - Episode 9: 1000 Subscribers Party!
